ayahs.wordByWord: وَٱتَّقُوا۟ [And fear] ٱلَّذِى [the One Who] خَلَقَكُمْ [created you] وَٱلْجِبِلَّةَ [and the generations] ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ [the former]
قَالُوٓا۟ [They said] إِنَّمَآ [Only] أَنتَ [you] مِنَ [(are) of] ٱلْمُسَحَّرِينَ [those bewitched]

ayahs.textUthmani: وَمَآ أَنتَ إِلَّا بَشَرٌ مِّثْلُنَا وَإِن نَّظُنُّكَ لَمِنَ ٱلْكَـٰذِبِينَ
ayahs.wordByWord: وَمَآ [And not] أَنتَ [you] إِلَّا [(are) except] بَشَرٌۭ [a man] مِّثْلُنَا [like us] وَإِن [and indeed] نَّظُنُّكَ [we think you] لَمِنَ [surely (are) of] ٱلْكَـٰذِبِينَ [the liars]
ayahs.transliteration: Wama anta illa basharunmithluna wa-in nathunnuka lamina alkathibeen

ayahs.textUthmani: فَأَسْقِطْ عَلَيْنَا كِسَفًا مِّنَ ٱلسَّمَآءِ إِن كُنتَ مِنَ ٱلصَّـٰدِقِينَ
ayahs.wordByWord: فَأَسْقِطْ [Then cause to fall] عَلَيْنَا [upon us] كِسَفًۭا [fragments] مِّنَ [of] ٱلسَّمَآءِ [the sky] إِن [if] كُنتَ [you are] مِنَ [of] ٱلصَّـٰدِقِينَ [the truthful]
ayahs.transliteration: Faasqit AAalayna kisafan minaassama-i in kunta mina assadiqeen

ayahs.wordByWord: قَالَ [He said] رَبِّىٓ [My Lord] أَعْلَمُ [knows best] بِمَا [of what] تَعْمَلُونَ [you do]

ayahs.textUthmani: فَكَذَّبُوهُ فَأَخَذَهُمْ عَذَابُ يَوْمِ ٱلظُّلَّةِ ۚ إِنَّهُۥ كَانَ عَذَابَ يَوْمٍ عَظِيمٍ
ayahs.wordByWord: فَكَذَّبُوهُ [But they denied him] فَأَخَذَهُمْ [so seized them] عَذَابُ [(the) punishment] يَوْمِ [(of the) day] ٱلظُّلَّةِ ۚ [(of) the shadow] إِنَّهُۥ [Indeed, it] كَانَ [was] عَذَابَ [(the) punishment] يَوْمٍ [(of) a Day] عَظِيمٍ [Great]
ayahs.transliteration: Fakaththaboohu faakhathahumAAathabu yawmi aththullati innahu kanaAAathaba yawmin AAatheem

ayahs.textUthmani: إِنَّ فِى ذَٰلِكَ لَـَٔايَةً ۖ وَمَا كَانَ أَكْثَرُهُم مُّؤْمِنِينَ
ayahs.wordByWord: إِنَّ [Indeed] فِى [in] ذَٰلِكَ [that] لَـَٔايَةًۭ ۖ [surely, is a sign] وَمَا [but not] كَانَ [are] أَكْثَرُهُم [most of them] مُّؤْمِنِينَ [believers]
ayahs.transliteration: Inna fee thalika laayatan wamakana aktharuhum mu/mineen

ayahs.wordByWord: وَإِنَّ [And indeed] رَبَّكَ [your Lord] لَهُوَ [surely, He] ٱلْعَزِيزُ [(is) the All-Mighty] ٱلرَّحِيمُ [the Most Merciful]
وَإِنَّهُۥ [And indeed, it] لَتَنزِيلُ [surely, is a Revelation] رَبِّ [(of the) Lord] ٱلْعَـٰلَمِينَ [(of) the worlds]
نَزَلَ [Has brought it down] بِهِ [Has brought it down] ٱلرُّوحُ [the Spirit] ٱلْأَمِينُ [[the] Trustworthy]
عَلَىٰ [Upon] قَلْبِكَ [your heart] لِتَكُونَ [that you may be] مِنَ [of] ٱلْمُنذِرِينَ [the warners]
بِلِسَانٍ [In language] عَرَبِىٍّۢ [Arabic] مُّبِينٍۢ [clear]
وَإِنَّهُۥ [And indeed, it] لَفِى [surely, (is) in] زُبُرِ [(the) Scriptures] ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ [(of) the former (people)]

ayahs.textUthmani: أَوَلَمْ يَكُن لَّهُمْ ءَايَةً أَن يَعْلَمَهُۥ عُلَمَـٰٓؤُا۟ بَنِىٓ إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ
ayahs.wordByWord: أَوَلَمْ [Is it not] يَكُن [Is it not] لَّهُمْ [to them] ءَايَةً [a sign] أَن [that] يَعْلَمَهُۥ [know it] عُلَمَـٰٓؤُا۟ [(the) scholars] بَنِىٓ [(of the) Children] إِسْرَٰٓءِيلَ [(of) Israel]
ayahs.transliteration: Awa lam yakun lahum ayatan anyaAAlamahu AAulamao banee isra-eel

ayahs.wordByWord: وَلَوْ [And if] نَزَّلْنَـٰهُ [We (had) revealed it] عَلَىٰ [to] بَعْضِ [any] ٱلْأَعْجَمِينَ [(of) the non-Arabs]

ayahs.textUthmani: فَقَرَأَهُۥ عَلَيْهِم مَّا كَانُوا۟ بِهِۦ مُؤْمِنِينَ
ayahs.wordByWord: فَقَرَأَهُۥ [And he (had) recited it] عَلَيْهِم [to them] مَّا [not] كَانُوا۟ [they would] بِهِۦ [in it] مُؤْمِنِينَ [(be) believers]
كَذَٰلِكَ [Thus] سَلَكْنَـٰهُ [We have inserted it] فِى [into] قُلُوبِ [(the) hearts] ٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ [(of) the criminals]

ayahs.textUthmani: لَا يُؤْمِنُونَ بِهِۦ حَتَّىٰ يَرَوُا۟ ٱلْعَذَابَ ٱلْأَلِيمَ
ayahs.wordByWord: لَا [Not] يُؤْمِنُونَ [they will believe] بِهِۦ [in it] حَتَّىٰ [until] يَرَوُا۟ [they see] ٱلْعَذَابَ [the punishment] ٱلْأَلِيمَ [[the] painful]
ayahs.transliteration: La yu/minoona bihi hattayarawoo alAAathaba al-aleem

ayahs.wordByWord: فَيَأْتِيَهُم [And it will come to them] بَغْتَةًۭ [suddenly] وَهُمْ [while they] لَا [(do) not] يَشْعُرُونَ [perceive]

words.translation: And it will come to them

ayahs.wordByWord: فَيَقُولُوا۟ [Then they will say] هَلْ [Are] نَحْنُ [we] مُنظَرُونَ [(to be) reprieved]
أَفَبِعَذَابِنَا [So is it for Our punishment] يَسْتَعْجِلُونَ [they wish to hasten]

words.translation: So is it for Our punishment

ayahs.wordByWord: أَفَرَءَيْتَ [Then have you seen] إِن [if] مَّتَّعْنَـٰهُمْ [We let them enjoy] سِنِينَ [(for) years]
ثُمَّ [Then] جَآءَهُم [comes to them] مَّا [what] كَانُوا۟ [they were] يُوعَدُونَ [promised]
